\v 12 Maruva aonekwa panyika;
\s Nguva yokurira kweshiri yasvika, Nezwi renjiva rinonzwika panyika
\s yedu.
\p
\v 13 Muonde woibvisa maonde awo mambishi,
\s Uye midzambiringa yotunga maruva; Yobudisa kunhuwira kwawo; Simuka, -shamwari yangu, akanaka
\s wangu huya!
\p
\v 14 Iwe njiva yangu, uri mumikaha yedombo,
\s Pakadzitika pamawere;
\s Ndione chiso chako,
\s Ndinzwe izwi rako;
\s Nokuti izwi rako rakanaka, chiso chako chakanaka.
\p
\v 15 Tibatirei makava, makava maduku, Anotadzira minda yemidzambiringa; Nokuti minda yedu
\s yemidzambiringa yotunga maruva.
\p
\v 16 Mudiwa wangu ndowangu, neni ndiri wake;
\s Anofudza makwai ake pakati pamaruva ebundo.
\p
\v 17 Kana zuva rotonhorera, nemimvuri yotiza,
\s Tendeuka, mudiwa wangu, uve semharapara nomwana wenondo Pamusoro pamakomo eBheteri.
